    <p class="mono text-[10px] tracking-widest opacity-50 mt-4 text-center">▸ PRODUCT THUMBNAIL ART — REPLACE WITH ROOSTER CREATIVE PRODUCT PHOTOGRAPHY AT BUILD TIME</p>
  </div>
